snippet.title: The most important announcement of my life
snippet.description:
First swell of season was the perfect opportunity to do a gender reveal at my favorite place in the world, Pe'ahi also known as Jaws!

Edited by: Kevin Wolf

Filmed by: Aaron Lynton, Jace Panebianco, Marc Chambers, Marcus Rodrigues, Slater Neborsky, Tucker Wooding, Kevin Wolf

Special Thanks to KITV News Hawaii and @Cariuma
